name: D.G.Pals
description:
D.G.P: New World Beta LIVE 23rd May & D.G.P: Legends Beta LIVE 31st May 2022!
Welcome to the D.G.Verse! Backed by Crypto.com Capital and Spartan Group, D.G.Pals is one of the first to redefine Web3 gaming with the first Interoperable NFT on the Cronos chain. The D.G.Pals Genesis Collection is the most privileged set of 10,000 NFT collection. Genesis NFT holders will be empowered with resources, airdrops and other perks to help the D.G.Pals Team build the D.G.Verse. You can check out how, by owning a Genesis D.G.Pal NFT, you can help expand Panterra, grow the player base and contribute to development on the D.G.Pals Whitepaper or website. On top of these exclusive privileges, these Genesis D.G.Pal NFTs can also participate in all of the games in the D.G.Verse like every other D.G.Pal NFTs.

name: CRO CROW
description:
CRO CROW is the very first NFT deployed on the Cronos Chain.

Edition #1 was minted on block #946, just 1 hour and 27 minutes after Cronos was launched.

The CRO CROW Ecosystem revolves around this historic NFT and the art of Alemf, the artist behind the crows and some other side collections.

These NFTs can be staked to The Forest to passively earn $CRO which is automatically distributed from secondary market royalties and other sources of income.

CAW CAW!

name: Boomer Squad
description: Collection of 8008 Boomers using crypto in the only way they know how. Everyone has felt like our Boomers at some point in their crypto journey but just like everyone else they will figure it out eventually. Founded by a fully doxed team of 11, Boomer Squad was established to build an ecosystem of on chain games, events, collections, and ecosystem developments that reflects value back to our Gen 0 Boomers through our Verified Distribution Contract called the "Mattress Fund" and Boomer DAO. Check out our GitBook for a full breakdown of everything already established and in the works in our ecosystem

3 generations of uniquely generated primates that make up the Primate World. The original Cronos Primate Business is a collection of 1000 primates that sold out in two minutes. The Primates along with Gorillas and Corrupted give staking, raffles, giveaways and more.

The best is yet to come with the claiming of 3D Voxel (versions of 2D Weird Apes), our play to earn, Legends of Weirdonite and more features to be announced to continue experimenting on-chain services in the future! Weird Apes do not give up because you either die as a Ape, or you live long enough to get Weird!
Visit our Discord to join our wonderful community!

Your Crazy Scientist can be rewarded in the following ecosystems:
1/ Crazy Critters Arena
2/ Lab DEX
3/ CERN (gamified staking)
4/ Growth Chambers
5/ Future projects
Within the Laboratory, we have a distinct focus on community. The Laboratory is allocating resources to building its community. A place where members can trust and rely on others in finding opportunities both in crypto and NFTs.

• Dao (Tao) as a term from East Asian philosophy, which represents the natural order of the universe, the greater whole, that unites all the individual elements of the universe.
Dr Dao, main collection, was born with the aim of uniting artists, developers and builders to improve Cronos Projects, providing Incubator services and giving a percentage back from minting revenues.
